name: Wartech
tagline: Collective artificial intelligence, massive war, edge technology - that is WarTech
body:
### Welcome to Wartech world
This is an immense world, populated by robots. Engulfed in local conflicts, local lords constantly trying to seize control of earth, space, water and subterrain territory. 
**You are warned!** You will not last long. We will conquer you. This is you last chance

### Authors and Contributors
Artem (@ents) and Anton (@antofik).
